ersion\": \"Air India is facing leadership issues and financial losses as it tries to recover from a crash.\",            \"english_title\": \"Air India Challenges\",            \"translated_version\": \"Air India enfrenta problemas de liderazgo y p\u00e9rdidas financieras mientras intenta recuperarse de un accidente.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Desaf\u00edos de Air India\"        }    ]}"